title: Plant Cell Diagram
description: An artistic representation of a plant cell, showcasing various organelles such as the nucleus, chloroplasts, and vacuoles, all enclosed within a green cell wall.

title: Molecular Structure of DNA
description: A 3D representation of a DNA molecule, showcasing its double helix structure. The image features colored spheres representing different atoms: red, green, and blue spheres likely represent various elements such as carbon, oxygen, and nitrogen, illustrating the complex arrangement of nucleotides that make up the DNA.

title: Bacterial Cells
description: A microscopic view of bacterial cells, depicted in vibrant colors. The bacteria are elongated and rod-shaped, with a pinkish hue against a purple background, showcasing their structure and arrangement.
